title: Grammar - numbers
--- 

I constantly need to remind myself of the grammar rules when dealing with numbers. Here's my summary:

## Numbers 1 and 2
- The number should agree with the noun in both case and gender. Note: the number is usually implied through the noun, so you don't have to explicitly mention the number
- كتابٌ (واحدٌ(
- قلمان (إثنان(


